Purpose

aplibs-dsp is a general purpose DSP library which forms the basis of the Audio Toolbox software and is also integrated into IP Studio

Dependencies

apf - git@git0.rd.bbc.co.uk:apf/apf.git
netcdf-bbc - git@git0.rd.bbc.co.uk:aplibs/netcdf-bbc.git (for SOFA file support)
netcdf-cxx4-bbc - git@git0.rd.bbc.co.uk:aplibs/netcdf-cxx4-bbc.git (for SOFA file support)

Files

autogen.sh - simple autotools script
configure.ac - configure configuration for autotools
COPYING - information on copying this library
debian/ - Debian control and version information
doxygen.am - Doxygen automake file
doxygen.cfg - Doxygen configuration
m4 - folder for autotools
Makefile.am - makefile for automake
README - this file
src/ - source folder containing C/C++ source and header files

src/3DPosition.cpp                      | 3D position and transformation classes
src/3DPosition.h                        |

src/ByteSwap.cpp                        | Byte swapping for endianness control
src/ByteSwap.h                          |

src/Convolver.cpp                       | Multi-channel parallelized and partitioned convolution using APF
src/Convolver.h                         |

src/Crossfader.cpp                      | Various kinds of aduio crossfades
src/Crossfader.hpp                      |

src/FractionalSample.cpp                | Fractional delay line for floating point samples
src/FractionalSample.h

src/genconversions.php                  | PHP script to GENERATE SoundFormatRawConverisons.cpp

src/Logging.hpp                         | Logging functionality

src/Makefile.am                         | Makefile for automake

src/misc.cpp                            | Miscelleanous functions and definitions, especially debugging functions
src/misc.h                              |

src/ParameterSet.cpp                    | A generic key=value handler with operators and comparators
src/ParameterSet.h                      |

src/PerformanceMonitor.cpp              | A multi-point logging runtime performance monitor (with outputs suitable for gnuplot)
src/PerformanceMonitor.h                |

src/PositionCursor.h                    | Interface for a 3D position cursor (i.e. tying positions to time)

src/readme.txt                          | Small readme file

src/SOFA.cpp                            | SOFA file support via the netcdf-bbc libraries
src/SOFA.h                              |

src/SoundDelayBuffer.cpp                | Delay/ring audio buffer 
src/SoundDelayBuffer.h                  |

src/SoundFormatConversions.cpp          | Sound sample format conversion/transfer routines
src/SoundFormatConversions.h            |

src/SoundFormatRawConversions.cpp       | AUTO-GENERATED (by genconversions.php) implementation of efficient sound format conversions
src/SoundFormatRawConversions.h         | (.h file not auto-generated)

src/SoundMixing.cpp                     | Sound summing functions
src/SoundMixing.h                       |

src/ThreadLock.cpp                      | Thread locking classes
src/ThreadLock.h                        |

src/VBAPanner2D.cpp                     | VBAP panner (2D version) 
src/VBAPanner2D.h                       |

src/VBAPanner.cpp                       | VBAP pannel (3D version)
src/VBAPanner.h                         |
